35 (12) To engage in research and development with respect to pollution control
36 facilities and solid waste or sewage disposal facilities, water facilities, resource recovery
37 facilities, and the development of energy resources;
38 (13) To collect rentals, fees, and other charges in connection with its services or for
39 the use of any project hereunder;
40 (14) To sell at private sale any of its property or projects to any private person, firm,
